了。<br/>\n这可比古时候的传道牛逼多了。   </p>\n<p>“援军不知道什么时候到达了”</p>\n", "last_modified": 1717373903, "replies": 80, "id": 1046198}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/92cc/2275/92_large.png?m=1582875070", "name": "chrome", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/92cc/2275/92_normal.png?m=1582875070", "title": "Chrome", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/chrome", "topics": 2086, "footer": "", "header": "Google Chrome is a browser that combines a minimal design with sophisticated technology to make the web faster, safer, and easier.", "title_alternative": "Chrome", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/92cc/2275/92_mini.png?m=1582875070", "stars": 1080, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 92, "parent_node_name": "browsers"}, "member": {"id": 560653, "username": "NIIIIIIIIIICE", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/NIIIIIIIIIICE", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_mini.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_normal.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_large.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_xlarge.png?m=1717319368", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1b6/cfba/560653_xlarge.png?m=1717319368", "created": 1635980254, "last_modified": 1717319368}, "last_reply_by": "body007", "last_touched": 1717386678, "title": "Chrome 将在明天推行均有争议的 Manifest V3 了 大量 Manifest V2 扩展将被禁用", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1046137", "created": 1717319752, "deleted": 0, "content": "最早从 2024 年 6 月的 Chrome 127 开始，我们将开始停用 Chrome 的不稳定版本（开发者版、Canary 版和 Beta 版）中的 Manifest V2 扩展程序。受此变化影响的用户会在浏览器中看到 Manifest V2 扩展程序自动停用，并且无法再从 Chrome 应用商店安装 Manifest V2 扩展程序。此外，Manifest V2 扩展程序在 Chrome 应用商店中将不再拥有“精选”徽章（如果目前已有该徽章）。\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n原文： https://developer.chrome.com/blog/resuming-the-transition-to-mv3?hl=zh-cn\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n检查了我工作生活会用到那些浏览器扩展，大部分都是 manifest V2 ，尤其是国内的😓看来又快要度过一个混乱时期了，已经禁止 Chrome 自动更新，看看情况再说。", "content_rendered": "<p>最早从 2024 年 6 月的 Chrome 127 开始，我们将开始停用 Chrome 的不稳定版本（开发者版、Canary 版和 Beta 版）中的 Manifest V2 扩展程序。受此变化影响的用户会在浏览器中看到 Manifest V2 扩展程序自动停用，并且无法再从 Chrome 应用商店安装 Manifest V2 扩展程序。此外，Manifest V2 扩展程序在 Chrome 应用商店中将不再拥有“精选”徽章（如果目前已有该徽章）。</p>\n<p>原文： <a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/blog/resuming-the-transition-to-mv3?hl=zh-cn\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://developer.chrome.com/blog/resuming-the-transition-to-mv3?hl=zh-cn</a></p>\n<p>检查了我工作生活会用到那些浏览器扩展，大部分都是 manifest V2 ，尤其是国内的😓看来又快要度过一个混乱时期了，已经禁止 Chrome 自动更新，看看情况再说。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1717319752, "replies": 73, "id": 1046137}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3417/3cb3/30_large.png?m=1598508698", "name": "chengdu", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3417/3cb3/30_normal.png?m=1598508698", "title": "成都", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/chengdu", "topics": 1479, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Chengdu", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3417/3cb3/30_mini.png?m=1598508698", "stars": 1155, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 30, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 685141, "username": "zbm1991", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zbm1991", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5aa6/07c2/685141_mini.png?m=1715392813", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5aa6/07c2/685141_normal.png?m=1715392813", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5aa6/07c2/685141_large.png?m=1715392813", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5aa6/07c2/685141_xlarge.png?m=1715392813", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5aa6/07c2/685141_xlarge.png?m=1715392813", "created": 1713142621, "last_modified": 1715392813}, "last_reply_by": "edisonwong", "last_touched": 1717387413, "title": "人在成都不能吃辣怎么办？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1046207", "created": 1717376245, "deleted": 0, "content": "山东人，北漂多年后来成都定居。但是完全不能吃辣，属于闻到辣味胃就隐隐作痛的感觉，吃一点就鼻涕停不下来的那种。请问有什么除湿的好办法，近来感觉美没精神。", "content_rendered": "<p>山东人，北漂多年后来成都定居。但是完全不能吃辣，属于闻到辣味胃就隐隐作痛的感觉，吃一点就鼻涕停不下来的那种。请问有什么除湿的好办法，近来感觉美没精神。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1717376245, "replies": 59, "id": 1046207}]